  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChainedFilter
    Represents a filter chain, allowing runtime reconfiguration of filters.
    ChainedFilterBuilder
    Utility class for building ChainedFilter objects, which chains multiple filters and allows reconfiguring filters by type as needed.
    DelegatedUniversalPcmAudioFilter
    Utility class that delegates all calls to a separate filter, used by UnlinkedChainedFilter.
    DelegatedUniversalPcmAudioFilter.NoopUniversalPcmAudioFilter
    Noop filter, which discards all data received.
    UnlinkedChainedFilter
    Chained filter whose output can be dynamically changed.
